      "title": "Sri Lanka's place in corruption",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka is ranked 102nd in Transparency International's (TI) most recent Corruption Perceptions Index (year 2021).",
        "The index ranks public sector corruption in 180 countries and territories around the world. Section 4 of the review report recommends that \"efforts should be continued to strengthen governance and reduce corrupt practices\"."
      ],
